Question: Sunlune Corporation CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Sunlune Corporation

JASMINER X16 Series

- Latest generation crypto mining products
- Utilizes 3D integrated memory and computing core chip technology
- Low power consumption, suitable for professional venues and home environments
- JASMINER X16-Q: 1950MH/s±10% hashrate, 620W±10% power consumption, 0.32J/MH±10% energy efficiency ratio
- JASMINER X16-P: Up to 5800MH/s hashrate, 1900W±10% power consumption, 0.32J/MH±10% energy efficiency ratio
- Supports ETCHASH and ETHASH algorithms
- 3U standard size, operates at a noise level of 40dB±10%
- Visitors can engage with company executives and experience the products firsthand at CES 2024 booth #9550
